@startuml group-assessment-flow
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam activityBackgroundColor #F0EEF8
skinparam activityBorderColor #3D108A
skinparam activityArrowColor #2E2E38
skinparam activityFontSize 13
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor #FFFBD6
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor #2E2E38
skinparam activityDiamondFontSize 13
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #E8F8F8
skinparam noteBorderColor #27ACAA
skinparam noteFontSize 12
skinparam swimlaneTitleFontSize 14
skinparam swimlaneBorderColor #2E2E38

title Group assessment flow: from department mapping to finalization

|#F0EEF8|Coordinator (Admin or Super Admin)|
start
:Create the bank's departments;
note right
  One-click seed of the five
  standard Tunisian departments
end note
:Invite Analysts, assigning
each to a department;
:Create the shared group
assessment draft;
|#E8F8F8|Platform (Postgres under RLS)|
:Enforce at most one
open draft per bank;
|#F0EEF8|Coordinator (Admin or Super Admin)|
:Map each dimension to
exactly one department;
note right
  Suggested Tunisian
  mapping available
end note
|#EAF4FD|Department Analysts|
:Open the group assessment view;
:See only the dimensions
assigned to their department;
repeat
  :Score an indicator (1 to 5)
  with evidence, or skip;
  note right
    Solo rules still apply:
    evidence cap (score of 3 or
    more without evidence
    computes as 2), skip ceiling
    of 20% per dimension,
    regulatory (BCT) indicators
    cannot be skipped
  end note
  |#E8F8F8|Platform (Postgres under RLS)|
  :Auto-save to the shared answer map;
  note right
    Write accepted only if: same bank,
    draft still open, and the indicator's
    true dimension is assigned to the
    analyst's department
  end note
  |#EAF4FD|Department Analysts|
repeat while (All assigned indicators\nanswered or skipped?) is (No)
-> Yes;
:"Your part is complete" banner;
|#F0EEF8|Coordinator (Admin or Super Admin)|
:Monitor per-dimension progress
and live headline scores;
:Confirm finalization;
|#E8F8F8|Platform (Postgres under RLS)|
:Re-read all answers and compute scores
with the shared scoring engine;
if (At least one indicator scored?) then (No)
  :Refuse finalization;
  stop
else (Yes)
endif
:Insert one immutable submission row
(snapshot of scores, answers, profile);
:Atomically flip the draft to finalized;
:Answers become read-only
at the database layer;
note right
  Unfilled dimensions drop out of the
  GMI through weight renormalization
end note
stop

@enduml
